Present at the Grand Palais, for the ceremony of handing over the Ballon d’Or 2018, Didier Deschamps returned to the coronation of the Blues in Russia at the microphone of the Chaîne L’Equipe: “It is the merit of the players above all. It gave a lot of joy and happiness to all the French people. There is nothing above the world champion title. All French are world champions. For four years at least. “And more if affinities … Meanwhile, Antoine Griezmann and Kylian Mbappé can always dream of the Ballon d’Or. In any case, they will be in the first four … Even if the Croatian Luka Modric seems to have to be sacred according to various indiscretions.
